1 (1) Shall reflect the applicable annual percentage change
2 in the increase of wharfage rates set by the
3 department of transportation's harbors division,
4 pursuant to applicable administrative rules;
5 (2) Shall be applied on an annual basis through June 30,
6 2029, in accordance with subsection (c);
7 (3) May be applied on an annual basis beginning July 1,
8 2029, through June 30, 2033, in accordance with
9 subsection (d); and
10 (4) Shall be not more than five per cent per year.
11 (c) Beginning on July 1, 2026, through June 30, 2029, the
12 commission shall apply the mechanism as follows:
13 (1) In the first and second years, the water carrier
14 inflationary cost index automatic adjustment mechanism
15 shall be applied annually; and
16 (2) For the third year of the three-year cycle, regardless
17 of whether the water carrier is seeking any rate
18 changes for the transportation of property, the water
19 carrier shall submit an application with the rates,
20 fares, or charges for the transportation of property
21 that the water carrier proposes to be effective in the
