5 (d) Beginning July 1, 2029, through June 30, 2033, the
6 commission may apply the mechanism as follows:
7 (1) In the first, second, and fourth years, the water
8 carrier inflationary cost index automatic adjustment
9 mechanism may be applied annually; and
10 (2) For the third year, regardless of whether the water
11 carrier is seeking any rate changes for the
12 transportation of property, the water carrier shall
13 submit an application with the rates, fares, or
14 charges for the transportation of property that the
15 water carrier proposes to be effective in the third
16 year. The application shall be subject to the review
17 and process requirements for a standard rate increase
18 application under section 271G-17(d) and (e).
19 (e) Customers eligible for preferential agricultural water
20 rates under section 269-26.5 shall be exempt from any automatic
21 adjustment mechanism authorized by this section.”
