1 SECTION 2. Section 271G-5, Hawaii Revised Statutes, is
2 amended by adding a new definition to be appropriately inserted
3 and to read as follows:
4 '"'Automatic adjustment mechanism” means any rate adjustment
5 mechanism that allows a water carrier to change rates between
6 rate cases."
